  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Material recovery event at an EPR-registered recycler. The",
    "returned trade-item instances enter the recycling stream and are",
    "transformed into a recovered material output (rPET flake).",
    "Modelled as an EPCIS TransformationEvent: inputEPCList carries",
    "the returned bottle instances; outputEPCList carries a new",
    "rPET-flake trade item identified by its own GTIN. The dpp:",
    "recycledContent statistics produced by this run live on the",
    "output product entry inside masterDataAvailableFor.",
    "",
    "PPWR Reg 2025/40 Title VII, Art. 47 (recycled-content claims)",
    "and the EPR registration link via dpp:extendedProducerResponsibility.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: dpp=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,",
    "                              ppwr=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/ppwr/",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
